flowchart TB
    %% Projection-friendly architecture diagram
    A[Student Portal] --> B[Authentication]
    B --> C[Profile Management]
    C --> D[Bursary Application]
    D --> E[Review Module]
    E --> F[Admin Approval]
    F --> G[Decision and Disbursement]

    D --> H[Notification Module]
    F --> H
    H --> I[Email Service SMTP]

    C --> J[(MySQL Database)]
    D --> J
    E --> J
    F --> J
    K[Reports and Dashboard] --> J

    subgraph L1 [Presentation Layer]
      A
      K
    end

    subgraph L2 [Application Layer]
      B
      C
      D
      E
      F
      H
    end

    subgraph L3 [Data and External Services]
      J
      I
      G
    end

